Package sc2002Project

Class SupToFYPReq

java.lang.Object
sc2002Project.Request
sc2002Project.SupToFYPReq
public class SupToFYPReq extends Request
This class represents a supervisor to FYP request. It extends the Request class and contains additional fields: Supervisor, FYP, Project and new Supervisor.
